      "index": 0,
      "text": "set %scores% = [{\u0022score\u0022:10}, {\u0022score\u0022:20}]",
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Regression anchor: with the \u0060where T : item\u0060 constraint locked and every value \u0060: item\u0060,\nsorting a list of dicts is still rejected \u2014 \u0060item\u0060 carries no ordering for dict to leak,\nregardless of the kind of the dict\u0027s values. PLang surfaces it as an error (not a thrown\nexception), so the on-error handler catches it.",
